{"tid":797814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"諗起老豆老母晚晚訓埋一張床幾廿年，佢地個仔就到死個日都自己一個訓，自己一個去，真係情願冇黎過世上","createTime":"2018-08-28T21:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T03:55:44.000Z","uid":58316,"like":10,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"68577f9f437d59deb17a139afa1e959fa344a496","tid":797814,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T21:07:25.000Z","msg":"晚晚四幢牆<br />\n擘大眼得自己一個<br />\n晚晚如是<br />\n出到去好似得個殼咁<br />\n揾完錢餵飽自己<br />\n返到黎又係得個坐字<br />\n由細到大<br />\n讀書揾野做<br />\n人地叫乜我做乜<br />\n交代完<br />\n每晚返到黎<br />\n情願俾人榨乾榨淨<br />\n返工俾人鬧到隻狗咁<br />\n當你傻仔咁舞<br />\n起碼都仲有野充塞下自己<br />\n坐係張床度<br />\n乜都冇<br />\n賓洲都費事玩<br />\n時間都係要過<br />\n時間都係會過<br />\n坐坐下就坐走大半世人<br />\n晚晚諗女人<br />\n晚晚攬住隻枕頭當係自己老婆<br />\n如果我去左<br />\n真係得返隻枕頭係會陪我行埋人生最後一段路"},{"pid":"b62c1421573c7a8a2b27cf4dd18163a3a8509763","tid":797814,"uid":16668,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T21:13:51.000Z","msg":"你呢家冇，你以後會有"},{"pid":"0874eb9709312a524accc10a9cb02693d3e6b167","tid":797814,"uid":154465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T21:19:02.000Z","msg":"23892222<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd2b58135e1d4ceff9a4b4f5c5fc385b100a1a6","tid":797814,"uid":101253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T21:19:29.000Z","msg":"去旅行啦"},{"pid":"0ce2821608baf8d6c8ce52b80876d603e0c27872","tid":797814,"uid":190258,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T21:23:57.000Z","msg":"開埋咁多癡線post，我係女見到你都調頭走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8e791e880564842b36a90365ae9ac173f9790f","tid":797814,"uid":162233,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T21:30:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"301c0efde2b625f21e4de1a0b5c3ac851c29dd09","tid":797814,"uid":127998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T21:37:53.000Z","msg":"無女叫春似足mk"},{"pid":"4702864bbd14432bfa69